snippet.title: Musapey's Choco Marker (Dreamcast) - Intro +  A-1 to A-3
snippet.description:
Intro and first three levels of Musapey's Choco Marker for the Sega Dreamcast.

For more footage of rare or obscure games, visit Brainstorm Warning at http://www.brainstormwarning.org

EDIT: In response to 
tabbyaboutroots: A demo of the PC version is available @ http://e56.info/choco/index.html
